accessibility.text: Chip Kidd, Great Neck Cover, 2003, Print

The book cover for Great Neck features a mix of styles. Kidd used photography that merges into a comic book style, with sharp contours, vivid colors, and illustration. It features a mix of a script typeface and a modern, sans-serif typeface. These brings the comic book style into the realm of reality by combining photography and illustration.
